description.name: Adaptors - pins for shop press
description.long_desc:
Suitable for use with presses with a female ram assembly diameter of 25 mm.


Product Features



  • Mounting hole: 25mm

  • Set of 8 pins and a stand

  • Handy storage for mounting directly on the hydraulic press


Pressing pins



  • Diameter 10 mm, Length 50 mm, Maximum capacity 2 T

  • Diameter 12 mm, Length 60 mm, Maximum capacity 3 T

  • Diameter 16 mm, Length 60 mm, Maximum capacity 8 T

  • Diameter 22 mm, Length 85 mm, Maximum capacity 16 T

  • Diameter 25 mm, Length 110 mm, Maximum capacity 18 T

  • Diameter 30 mm, Length 110 mm, Maximum capacity 20 T
